import { Component } from "react";
import { Row, Col, Container, Card, ListGroup } from "react-bootstrap";

class Content extends Component {
    render() {

        return (
            <Row>
                <Col className="d-none d-sm-block" sm={2} md={2} style={{ border: "1px solid green" }}>Left</Col>
                <Col sm={10} md={8} style={{ border: "1px solid green", padding: "0px" }}>
                    <Container fluid>
                        <Row>
                            <Col sm={6} md={3} style={{ padding: "10px" }}>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/flying.jpeg" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 1</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $10
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 10 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                            <Col style={{ padding: "10px" }}>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/huaweip30.png" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 2</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $200
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 15 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                            <Col>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/iphonex.jpeg" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 3</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $200
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 15 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                            <Col>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/oppf19.png" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 2</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $200
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 15 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                            <Col>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/iphonex.jpeg" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 3</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $200
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 15 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                            <Col>
                                <Card style={{ width: '100%' }}>
                                    <Card.Img src="/products/iphonex.jpeg" style={{ height: "200px" }} />
                                    <Card.Body style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                                        <Card.Title>
                                            <Card.Link href="#">Product 3</Card.Link>
                                        </Card.Title>
                                        <Card.Text>
                                            Price: $200
                                        </Card.Text>
                                    </Card.Body>
                                    <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
                                        <ListGroup.Item>Discount: 15 %</ListGroup.Item>
                                    </ListGroup>
                                </Card>
                            </Col>
                        </Row>
                    </Container>
                </Col>
                <Col className="d-none d-sm-none d-md-block" md={2} style={{ border: "1px solid green" }}>Right</Col>
            </Row>
        );
    }
}

export default Content;
